functions.remarks:
Use `WithPersistence` to adjust Garnet persistence configuration, e.g.:
```
var garnet = builder.AddGarnet("garnet")
.WithDataBindMount("mydata")
.WithPersistence(TimeSpan.FromSeconds(10));
```

Use `WithPersistence` to adjust Garnet persistence configuration, e.g.:
```
var cache = builder.AddGarnet("cache")
.WithDataVolume()
.WithPersistence(TimeSpan.FromSeconds(10));
```

